              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: itī śrībhaviṣyottarapurāṇe upāṃgalalitāvratasa[ṃ]pūrṇa[ṃ] // cha // // idaṃ pustakaṃ mathurānāthadevena likhitaṃ ātmapaṭhanārthaṃ paropakārārthaṃ // cha (f. 11v).</colophon>
